.Dd June 2, 2026
.Dt SC 1
.Os
.Sh NAME
.Nm sc
.Nd send a control command to musicd
.Sh SYNOPSIS
.Nm
.Fl s Ar socket-path
.Ar command
.Op Ar args ...
.Sh DESCRIPTION
.Nm
connects to the
.Xr musicd 1
Unix-domain socket at
.Ar socket-path
and sends
.Ar command .
.Pp
For
.Cm list
and
.Cm status ,
.Nm
copies the daemon response to standard output.
.Sh COMMANDS
.Nm
accepts these commands:
.Cm exit ,
.Cm list ,
.Cm loop ,
.Cm consume ,
.Cm pause ,
.Cm play ,
.Cm skip ,
.Cm stop ,
.Cm toggle ,
.Cm status ,
.Cm volume ,
and
.Cm clear .
.Sh SEE ALSO
.Xr musicd 1 ,
.Xr sq 1
